HEADWORD: Saur
<hw>Saur</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Contracted from Gael.
<ets>salachar</ets> filth, nastiness, fr. <ets>salach</ets> nasty, fr.
<ets>sal</ets> filth, refuse.]</ety> <def>Soil; dirt; dirty water; urine
from a cowhouse.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
